title: Police chase ends in crash in Sydney's west | 7NEWS
description: A police chase in Sydney's western suburbs concluded when a fleeing Commodore ute collided with a BMW SUV at the intersection of Hector Street and Spencer Street in Sefton. The 44-year-old BMW driver was unharmed, and the arrested driver is scheduled to face court.
